
Add To Every thing
  Is
    clean.

  Verb clean
    Does Only
      "You clean the"
      If o Is clean Then
        Say o.
      Else 
        Make o clean.
        "dirty $o"
      End If.
      "enthusiastically."
  End Verb.


End Add To.


