End The aaa.

The gizmo Isa object
  At aaa
  Is 
    Not clean.
  Description
    "There is a"
    If gizmo Is Not clean Then
      "dirty"
    End If.
    "gizmo here."
  
End The gizmo.

Syntax clean = clean (o).

